## 1. WHAT THE PLATFORM IS

Mirellé Inspo is a nail editorial and business directory platform. It creates SEO-ranked posts on mirelleinspo.com to help nail businesses get discovered on Google. Businesses pay to be featured in posts that rank locally and nationally.

**Two post types:**
- **Type A — Client Acquisition Posts:** Created by Mirellé to attract paying clients. Rank on Google when business owners search for growth. End with a mailto CTA to contact@mirelleinspo.com
- **Type B — Deliverable Posts:** Created for paying clients once they order. Generated only when an order is placed. Not planned in the content system yet.

