## 6. TIER STRUCTURE

- **Tier 1 — Listing:** Small fee. Featured inside an existing roundup or directory post.
- **Tier 2 — Dedicated Post:** Medium fee. Own standalone post on the platform.
- **Tier 3 — Campaign:** Larger fee. Multiple posts over weeks or months. Client picks post types and duration. Preset packages available.

