## 8. TWO POST TYPES EXPLAINED

### Type A — Client Acquisition Posts (Current Focus)
Posts YOU create to rank on Google and attract paying clients.

**8-component structure — fixed:**
1. SEO Title — exact search phrase they type
2. Hook — one line hitting their pain point
3. Pain Block — 2-3 paragraphs in their language
4. Solution Bridge — introduce Mirellé editorially, not salesy
5. What You Offer Block — 3-4 bullets, what they get
6. Stats / Credibility Block — 3 real market stats
7. FAQ Section — 3-5 real objections answered honestly
8. CTA — mailto button to contact@mirelleinspo.com

### Type B — Deliverable Posts (On Order Only)
Posts created for paying clients once they order. Not in the content system yet.

